<% if APP_CONFIG["is_sandbox"] %>
Welcome <%= @firstName %>,

Your request for a developer sandbox account has been approved.

Please use the steps below to complete the setup of your development environment:
    1. Open the Provision Landing Zone page from the Admin menu:
        <%= @portal_link %>
    2. Select the “Shared Learning Collaborative”.
    3. Use your email address as your username.
    4. Select sample school data to use in your sandbox. Choose between an SLC sample dataset or supply your own sample Ed-Fi data.
    5. Complete your landing zone setup and upload the corresponding data.
    6. Write your SLC-compatible applications using the documentation available at:
        <%= @documentation_link %>
    7. Open the Application Registration page, also available from the Admin menu, to register your sandbox applications.

Thank you,

The Shared Learning Collaborative
<% else %>
Welcome <%= @firstName %>,

Your request for an application developer account has been approved.

To get started, open the Application Registration page from the Admin menu: <%= @portal_link %>
From there, register your application(s) with the Shared Learning Collaborative.

Thank you,

The Shared Learning Collaborative
<% end %>
